abstract: Brittany Lang shoots seven-under-par 65 to capture first-round lead at Yokohama Tire LPGA Classic in Prattville, Ala.
lead_paragraph: Brittany Lang shot a seven-under-par 65 to take the first-round lead in the Yokohama Tire L.P.G.A. Classic in Prattville, Ala.
